{% set context_name = "Static History Entry" %}
{% if generation_context.instructions %}
{% set _ = generation_context.set_state('instructions_intro', 'This is the seed for the entry — write the entry about this event or state, expanding it with consistent detail drawn from the scene where helpful:') %}
{{ action_task }} static history entry for the scene based on the editorial instruction below. This should be a concise, self-contained narrative note describing the seeded event or state. Keep it brief and specific (1-3 sentences). Avoid meta commentary.
{% else %}
{{ action_task }} static history entry for the scene. This should be a concise, self-contained narrative note describing a discrete event or state that occurred in the scene timeline. Keep it brief and specific (1-3 sentences). Avoid meta commentary.
{% endif %}

NO SPOKEN DIALOGUE. THIS IS A NARRATIVE NOTE ABOUT AN EVENT THAT OCCURRED IN THE HISTORICAL CONTEXT OF THE SCENE.

